      "review_summary": "The PR replaces selected provider success JSON parses in Vydra, xAI, Runway, PixVerse, DeepInfra, Together, ElevenLabs, Microsoft speech, and Microsoft Foundry with local 1 MiB `readResponseWithLimit` reads and adds generic bounded-reader proof/tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +93, Tests +247. Total +340 across 16 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current main still has direct successful `response.json()` reads in several targeted external-provider paths, and the PR body demonstrates generic bounded-reader cancellation versus unbounded buffering. I did not execute a live OOM reproduction in this read-only review.",
